				<td colspan="2"><span>f1f1,f2f2,......
<br />

<br />
use arow keys on keypad for movements
<br />

<br />
dedicated arrow keys are set to straif
<br />

<br />
mouse to look around and target and or instrument/weapon swap
<br />

<br />
targetting remapped to edit keys (instert/home/pageup, etc)
<br />

<br />
keypad &lt;+&gt;to target nearest mob
<br />
keypad &lt;enter&gt; for attack
<br />

<br />
macros
<br />
1-ss boots 2-fade or /pet attack
<br />
3-primary slot 4-secondary slot
<br />
5-bag with stuff for 3 and 4
<br />
6-10 depends on pulling, assisting, slowing, relevant messages go here</span></td>
